Help and support
How are matches generated?
They are generated by proximity that is the people who appear when you match are people close to you.
Can I search for specific profiles?
No you cannot search for specific profiles.
Are there filters to customize search preferences?
Yes you can add filters to the search such as age etc.
How are profiles updated or modified?
In the profile section within the main screen you can modify the profile characteristics.
Is there a feature to highlight common interests?
There are interests between people but it is not possible to highlight them.
What is the customer support process?
You can contact us by email.
Is there a helpline or live chat?
At the moment it is not implemented.
What resources are available to resolve technical issues?
By email we solve any problems you may have.
Does the app offer any profile creation assistance?
The application guide specifies how to create a user.
Are there events or social activities organized through the app?
The application is not responsible for events between people.
How do I start conversations with other users?
Once the two people have "matched" on the chat screen, said person will appear so you can talk.
Are there secure communication tools?
All communication between people is encrypted.
Can inappropriate profiles be blocked or reported?
Yes inappropriate profiles can be blocked.
Are there options for privacy in conversations?
No privacy is our priority and all conversations are encrypted.
Does the app offer tips or advice to break the ice?
You're going to have to manage, kid.
How is the security of personal information guaranteed?
All chat and personal information is encrypted.
What security measures are in place to avoid fake profiles or fraud?
They can be reported and immediately when we review it the account will be deleted.
Can I control who can see my profile?
No that information cannot be consulted.
Is there a security filter to protect older users?
Security is the same for everyone meaning there is no problem.
How is sensitive data handled in the application?
If we detect information that should not belong to the application, it will be deleted.
How does the application work?
Using the different sections of it such as chatting with people, etc.
What is the registration process?
Entering full name email password and age.
How are profiles created and personalized?
When you log out you can create another profile again or log in with an existing one.
What features and tools does the app offer?
You can create a profile, search for people to find love with chat with them modify your profile etc.
Is there a tutorial or user guide available?
No at the moment there is no user tutorial available.
